metadata.name: LUKE BOX
metadata.description:
LUKE BOX 

"Ah so that's where I left this!" -LUKE

Nostalgia reimagined by FRENS COLLECTIVE to build a strong and inclusive community of artists, collectors, and enthusiasts who support each other and value the power of adventure.

Our first stealth drop monuments a piece of NFT culture, allowing a claimable edition for all active communities. A token of appreciation and mystery...

Every journey begins with a choice!
